{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0426c40648","title":"关于阅处高岗起草的致苏联政府文件的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"747c582bdd","index":0,"year":1953,"month":9,"day":27,"articleId":"0426c40648"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"af71a4eedb","name":"高岗","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[{"id":"26830807c8","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"0426c40648","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指高岗起草的给苏联政府的文件。主要内容是对1952年8月11日签订的《苏联在1953年至1955年给予中华人民共和国在恢复与改建鞍山钢铁公司方面以技术援助的议定书》所规定的设计和设备交付期限，提出我方的意见，请苏联政府予以考虑，以便我国于1956年和1957年相当地增加轧钢能力，并基本上消灭炼钢能力和轧钢能力的不平衡现象，从而保证我国第一个五年计划中钢材的供应。"},{"id":"832aaae24f","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"0426c40648","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指苏联驻华大使库兹湿佐夫。"}],"contents":[{"id":"8685b10019","type":"title","text":"关于阅处高岗\"起草的致苏联政府文件的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"0426c40648"},{"id":"26830807c8","type":"paragraph","text":"周总理：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"0426c40648"},{"id":"832aaae24f","type":"paragraph","text":"此件是高岗同志根据他于今年去苏时和苏联当局的谈话起草的一个致苏联政府的文件，请你加以审查，以说帖方式，于你休假以前，交与库大使，请他转致苏联政府。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"0426c40648"},{"id":"e9739aa051","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"0426c40648"},{"id":"e2cc577e52","type":"paragraph","text":"九月廿七日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"0426c40648"},{"id":"448f5134d3","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]高岗，当时任中央人民政府国家计划委员会主席。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"0426c40648"}],"page":{"id":"04363296e8","pu